    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate CFD model capability to predict pump-induced hemolysis within pre-specified acceptance thresholds across all five operating conditions. RH < 1.0 at all operating points satisfies the COU acceptance criterion. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for this Class II CPB device.",
